  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Хичээл тарсны дараа&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;бүлэг хүүхэд Поликарпад төрсөн өдрийн мэнд хүргэхээр гэрт рүү нь явжээ.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: italic; color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">i</span>-р бүлэгт&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Element-3-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: black !important;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-7\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.031em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 0.76em; height: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-style: italic; word-spacing: normal;\">s</span><span style=\"font-style: italic; word-spacing: normal;\">i</span><span style=\"font-style: italic; word-spacing: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></span>(<span id=\"MathJax-Element-4-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: black !important;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-12\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 5.739em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 4.332em; height: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-14\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">1</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-15\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span style=\"font-style: italic; word-spacing: normal;\">s</span><span style=\"font-style: italic; word-spacing: normal;\">i</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-19\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-20\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">4)</span></span></span></span>&nbsp;хүүхэд байгаа ба тэд хамтдаа явахыг хүсэж байгаа. Тэд такси барихаар шийдсэн ба таксинд хамгийн ихдээ 4 хүн багтана.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Тийм бол бүх хүүхдүүдийг авч явахын тулд хамгийн цөөндөө хэдэн такси хэрэгтэй вэ? Бүлэг бүрийн хүүхдүүд нэг таксинд сууж явах ёстой ба нэг таксинд олон бүлэг багтааж болно.</span></p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;Эхний мөрөнд бүлгийн тоо</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; font-family: MathJax_Math; font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">n</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-6-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-24\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 6.821em;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 5.143em; height: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-26\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main;\">1</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-27\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-28\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Math; font-style: italic;\">n</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-29\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main;\">≤</span><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: MathJax_Main; font-size: 13px;\"><sup>5</sup></span><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px; font-family: MathJax_Main;\"><br></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">). Дараагийн мөрөнд&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: MathJax_Math; font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">n</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;ширхэг&nbsp;</span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-8-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-36\" style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 1.031em;\"><span style=\"transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; width: 0.76em; height: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: MathJax_Math; font-style: italic;\">s</span><span style=\"font-family: MathJax_Math; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic;\">i</span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;тоо.</span></p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Бүх хүүхдийг багтааж чадах хамгийн цөөн таксины тоо.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 1:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">5<br>1 2 4 3 3</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <strong>Output 1:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4</span></p>\n<p><strong>Input 2:</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">8<br>2 3 4 4 2 1 3 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Output 2:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">5</span></p>",
  "bodyText": "Хичээл тарсны дараа n бүлэг хүүхэд Поликарпад төрсөн өдрийн мэнд хүргэхээр гэрт рүү нь явжээ. i-р бүлэгт si(1≤si≤4) хүүхэд байгаа ба тэд хамтдаа явахыг хүсэж байгаа. Тэд такси барихаар шийдсэн ба таксинд хамгийн ихдээ 4 хүн багтана.\nТийм бол бүх хүүхдүүдийг авч явахын тулд хамгийн цөөндөө хэдэн такси хэрэгтэй вэ? Бүлэг бүрийн хүүхдүүд нэг таксинд сууж явах ёстой ба нэг таксинд олон бүлэг багтааж болно.\nInput\n Эхний мөрөнд бүлгийн тоо n (1≤n≤105). Дараагийн мөрөнд n ширхэг si тоо.\nOutput\nБүх хүүхдийг багтааж чадах хамгийн цөөн таксины тоо.\nExample\nInput 1: \n51 2 4 3 3\n Output 1: \n4\nInput 2:\n82 3 4 4 2 1 3 1\nOutput 2:\n5",
